      <name>Intelligence Summary</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture and activity patterns suggest a high level of operational tempo, with multiple aircraft and vessels engaged in various missions worldwide. The presence of carrier strike groups and amphibious ready groups in key regions indicates a strong naval presence, while the deployment of destroyers and cruisers suggests a focus on maritime security and deterrence. The intelligence summary also highlights the importance of unmanned systems, with several countries investing in maritime drone capabilities. Overall, the data suggests a complex and dynamic security environment, with multiple actors and interests at play.</description>
